<section class="about section" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="about-paragraph">
          I'm an Assistant Professor in the Department of Computer Science at University Name, 
          where I lead the Human-Centered Computing Lab. My research sits at the intersection of 
          human-computer interaction, accessibility, and machine learning.
        </p>
        <p class="about-paragraph">
          Before joining University Name, I completed my Ph.D. at MIT, where I was advised by 
          Professor John Doe. My dissertation focused on developing adaptive learning systems 
          that personalize educational content based on individual learning patterns and accessibility needs.
        </p>
        <p class="about-paragraph">
          I'm passionate about creating technology that empowers all learners, regardless of their 
          abilities or backgrounds. My work has been published in top-tier venues including CHI, 
          UIST, and ASSETS, and has been recognized with several awards including the Best Paper 
          Award at CHI 2023.
        </p>
        
        <div class="about-stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-number">25+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Publications</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-number">5</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Awards</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-number">10+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">PhD Students</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="about-image">
        <img 
          src="/placeholder.svg?height=500&width=400" 
          alt="Profile photo"
          class="profile-image"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background-color: var(--color-background);
  }
  
  .section-title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3xl);
  }
  
  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--spacing-3xl);
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .about-text {
    flex: 1;
  }
  
  .about-paragraph {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
  
  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
    padding-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  
  .stat {
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }
  
  .stat-label {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  
  .about-image {
    flex: 0 0 350px;
  }
  
  .profile-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .about-content {
      flex-direction: column-reverse;
    }
    
    .about-image {
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      max-width: 300px;
    }
    
    .about-stats {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>
